  "title": "Perfect Price Discrimination",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH958521.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">If the monopolist engages in perfect price discrimination, which of the following will happen?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Consumer surplus will remain the same <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"(a, plus b)\"><math alttext=\"(a, plus b)\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mstyle><mrow><mtext>a</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>b</mtext></mrow></mstyle><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span> and producer surplus will increase by area <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"(e)\"><math alttext=\"(e)\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mstyle><mrow><mtext>e</mtext></mrow></mstyle><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Both consumer surplus and producer surplus will decrease by area <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"(a, plus b, plus c, plus d)\"><math alttext=\"(a, plus b, plus c, plus d)\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mstyle><mrow><mtext>a</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>b</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>c</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>d</mtext></mrow></mstyle><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span>, and the deadweight loss will remain constant.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Consumer surplus will increase by area <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"(e)\"><math alttext=\"(e)\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mstyle><mrow><mtext>e</mtext></mrow></mstyle><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span>, producer surplus will decrease by area <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"(e)\"><math alttext=\"(e)\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mstyle><mrow><mtext>e</mtext></mrow></mstyle><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span>, and the deadweight loss will be zero.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Consumer surplus and deadweight loss will be zero because all economic surplus will be transferred to producer surplus.</p>\n",
        "value": "i4"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Both consumer surplus and producer surplus will increase because output produced will increase to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q sub 2\"><math alttext=\"Q sub 2\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i5"
      }
    ]
